-- Merkel to Discuss Euro Debt-Crisis With Sarkozy This Evening on Phone-Call
-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 2010-11-25T08:54:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-25/merkel-to-discuss-euro-debt-crisis-with-sarkozy-this-evening-on-phone-call.html
German Chancellor Angela Merkel will
discuss the euro-area economy in a phone call with French
President Nicolas Sarkozy early this evening, the German
government said.  A statement will probably be released after that with some
details of the call, the government spokeswoman said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
